enhanced_by.reason: Both methods require similar setup involving BaseProviders and IdNumberRequest for generating ID numbers.
Both methods involve generating a base part of the ID number, which is a critical step in the process.
The generateInvalid method modifies the checksum to make the ID number invalid, making checksum a key method for assertions.
The generateValid method can be used to compare against the invalid ID generated by generateInvalid to ensure the invalidity is correctly implemented.
